  <brief_title>Pilot Trial of Antibiotics Versus Surgery for Treating Acute Appendicitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Study for a Randomized Trial of Antibiotics Versus Surgery for Treatment of Patients With Acute Uncomplicated Appendicitis</official_title>
